e-run `./gradlew javaTest -Pcoordinates=com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2` and then `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2`.\n3. If native verification still fails after the test fix, inspect the two `native-test-verify` logs above and address the missing resource registrations separately from the library test change."}}
